<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Marlborough Park</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A charming residential neighborhood located within the northeast quadrant of Calgary, Marlborough Park is bound by the Memorial Drive on the south, the Trans-Canada Highway on the north, 52 Street E on the west and the 68 Street E on the east.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Developed back in 1972, the community in Marlborough Park is primarily popular for the enormous homonymous park which is located at the centre of the neighborhood. </p>
        </div>
